				"paragraphStyle" : {
					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "To exemplify the use of the LZA editor and model, we use the sample from  [landing-zone-accelerator-on-aws-for-healthcare](https://github.com/aws-samples/landing-zone-accelerator-on-aws-for-healthcare). This snippet updates the code from the repository locally:"
			},
